soooo drunk right now...<br>
sooo just got done reading Druid Grove Boards....<br>
<br>
Kiddies and Kerns, I Have a Dream...that one day, a little Druid and a little Mage will sit together in peace and harmony.  I have a dream that the little Druid will cry and moan to the Mage about how they need more Phat Lewts and how they need better spells than the Mage just as the Druid has been spamming and complaining for the last three years.....<br>
<br>
And that little Mage will be angry and annoyed, as all Mages have been over the the greed of the Druids.  But, my friends, my dream does not end there...<br>
<br>
Fellow Mages, I have a dream that the little Mage will get up, still choking back Flames, and go out in search of the biggest, sturdiest Nerf Bat that he can find and I have a dream that he will return to where that little Druid sits, spamming away about the Phat Lewts and Spells that he does not own....<br>
<br>
Kiddies and Kerns, I Have A Dream that the little Mage will commence to whaling on that little Druid's hide with that Nerf Bat like he's never been beat on before in his life.  I Have A Dream that he will beat that little Druid like a red-headed stepchild until he soils his Leggings Of Judgement.<br>
<br>
And after that little Mage starts beating on that little Druid, I Have A Dream that he will not Stop, Kiddies and Kerns, until that little Druid has been wacked upside and downside, Nerfed within an inch of his Tree-Hugging life, and he crawls all the way home to his mama, crying his eyes out, wishing by God in Heaven that he had never, ever whined about Phat Lewts and Spells to that little Mage.<br>
<br>
And I Have A Dream that the little Druid will learn a lesson he will never forget.  I have a dream that he will never, ever, ever whine or spam or cry about class balancing again to any Mages ever again in all his living days on Sony Online Entertainment's green Norrath under his respective Server.<br>
<br>
This Dream was brought to you by The Onion and Jack Daniels.<br>
<br>
